sequenceDiagram
    autonumber

    participant MA as MainActivity
    participant NCH as NativeCallHook
    participant Linker as ART / Bionic Linker
    participant Core as libnativecallhook.so
    participant BH as ByteHook
    participant LibA as lib_a.so
    participant LibB as lib_b.so

    Note over MA,LibB: Phase 1 — Hook Installation

    MA->>NCH: initialize()
    NCH->>Linker: System.loadLibrary("nativecallhook")
    Linker->>Core: load + run __attribute__((constructor))
    activate Core
    Core->>BH: bytehook_init()
    Core->>BH: bytehook_hook_all("__loader_dlopen", hooked_dlopen)
    BH-->>Core: stub handle
    deactivate Core
    Linker-->>NCH: library loaded
    NCH-->>MA: true

    MA->>Linker: System.loadLibrary("liba")
    Linker->>LibA: load (not in registry, normal path)

    Note over MA,LibB: Phase 2 — Intercepted Native-to-Native Loading

    MA->>LibA: testLibraryLoading() [JNI call]
    activate LibA
    LibA->>Linker: dlopen("lib_b.so")
    Linker->>Core: hooked_dlopen("lib_b.so")

    activate Core
    Note right of Core: Registry lookup → protected

    Core->>Core: Read encrypted file from disk,<br/>XOR decrypt, verify ELF header
    Core->>Core: memfd_create + write decrypted bytes

    Core->>Linker: android_dlopen_ext(LIBRARY_FD, memfd)
    Linker->>LibB: map from memfd, init, resolve symbols
    Linker-->>Core: library handle
    Core-->>LibA: handle
    deactivate Core

    LibA->>LibA: dlsym(handle, "call_logcat")
    LibA->>LibB: call_logcat()
    LibB-->>LibA: result
    deactivate LibA

    LibA->>ART: dlclose(handle)
    deactivate LibA

    LibA-->>MA: testLibraryLoading() returns
